00:41:34,409 --> 00:41:39,539
-我们叫他ai。-你好，你好。
- We call him ai. - Hello, ai hello.

290
00:41:45,420 --> 00:41:48,089
不,混乱关系。
No, tre.

291
00:42:14,657 --> 00:42:16,159
Documenti, Documenti !
Documenti, documenti!

292
00:42:16,409 --> 00:42:17,869
杀了香烟。
Kill the cigarettes.

293
00:42:21,831 --> 00:42:23,541
您看!您看!
Presto! Presto!

294
00:44:32,461 --> 00:44:35,298
-我不会说意大利语，一个都不会?
- I don't talk Italian - not even any?

295
00:44:35,381 --> 00:44:37,300
我知道但丁的一节诗。
I know one verse from Dante.

296
00:44:39,302 --> 00:44:42,513
你这次的任务是什么?
What kind of a mission do you make this time?

297
00:44:42,555 --> 00:44:44,724
你穿得连德国医生都不合适。
You're not even dressed right for a German doctor.

298
00:44:44,807 --> 00:44:47,560
哦,别担心。我会成为一个德国医生的。
Oh, don't worry. I'll be a German doctor all right.

299
00:44:47,643 --> 00:44:51,105
波达知道他要来吗?
Does polda know he's coming?

300
00:44:51,189 --> 00:44:53,441
我们要给他一个惊喜。
We're going to surprise him.

301
00:44:53,524 --> 00:44:57,528
——这是疯了。-这是一个非常重要的任务。
- That's crazy. - This is a very important mission.

302
00:45:01,157 --> 00:45:05,328
非常。我们所有人都有一个工作要做。
Very. All of us have one job to do.

303
00:45:05,411 --> 00:45:09,373
那就是把ai安全带进去见波达医生，然后再把他带出来。
That's to take ai safely in to see Dr. Polda, and then take him out again.

304
00:45:13,794 --> 00:45:16,464
好吧。
All right.

305
00:45:16,547 --> 00:45:20,384
现在波尔达总是从实验室回家吃午饭。
Now polda always comes home from his laboratory for noon dinner.

306
00:45:20,426 --> 00:45:24,013
之后，他睡了一个小时。然后他在他的书房工作。
After that, he sleeps for one hour. Then he works in his study.

307
00:45:24,096 --> 00:45:26,098
他下午有客人吗?
Does he have visitors in the afternoon?

308
00:45:28,059 --> 00:45:32,647
在我观察房子并得到报告的十天里，只有三个人来过。
Well, in the ten days I watched the house and get reports, only three visitors came.

309
00:45:32,688 --> 00:45:37,068
-谁在房子里?——一个管家。老女人，善良，愚蠢。
- Who's in the house? - A housekeeper. Old woman, nice, stupid.

310
00:45:37,151 --> 00:45:40,821
一个厨师。好厨师。法西斯。
A cook. Good cook. Fascist.

311
00:45:40,863 --> 00:45:46,160
还有四个秘密警察。Ovra男人。两天。两个晚上。
And four secret police. Ovra men. Two for day. Two for night.

312
00:45:46,244 --> 00:45:48,537
-其中的首领是路易吉。-检查完毕了吗?
- And the chief of them is Luigi. - Is it all checked?

313
00:45:48,621 --> 00:45:52,083
有天晚上我把他灌醉了，他问过我。
Checked from the cook when I got him drunk one night.

314
00:45:52,166 --> 00:45:54,835
从和我们在一起的波尔达牙医罗摩里医生那里查到的。
Checked from Dr. Romoli, dentist of polda who is with us.

315
00:45:54,919 --> 00:45:58,965
每天都被马soli和他的行为所检查，被我的眼睛所检查。
Checked by marsoli and his ways and checked by my eyes every day.

316
00:46:00,258 --> 00:46:02,927
现在你知道一流的信使能做什么了。
Now you know what a first-rate courier can do.

317
00:46:03,010 --> 00:46:06,013
你很擅长这个，战后我会给你找份工作。
You're so good at this, I'll get you a job at it after the war.

318
00:46:06,055 --> 00:46:08,516
-我不喜欢你那样说话。-我只是开个玩笑。
- I don't like you to talk like that. - I was only joking.

319
00:46:08,599 --> 00:46:12,436
-我不喜欢你开玩笑。——我很抱歉。
- I don't like yourjoking. - I'm sorry.

320
00:46:12,520 --> 00:46:16,941
-你对路易吉了解多少?-一个聪明人。训练有素。
- What do you know about Luigi? - A smart man. Well trained.

321
00:46:16,983 --> 00:46:19,777
这是令人欣慰的。
That's comforting.

322
00:46:19,860 --> 00:46:21,779
我怎么去房子呢?
How do I get to the house itself?

323
00:46:21,862 --> 00:46:26,826
去房子的事已经安排好了。但要想进去……
To get to the house has been arranged. But to get inside...

324
00:47:12,621 --> 00:47:16,417
威廉二世研究所的纳尔海姆博士来见波尔达教授。
Dr. Nalheim from kaiser Wilhelm institute to see professor polda.

325
00:47:22,715 --> 00:47:27,386
威廉二世研究所的纳尔海姆博士来见波尔达教授。
Dr. Nalheim from kaiser Wilhelm institute to see professor polda.

326
00:47:27,470 --> 00:47:30,056
——Passaporto。-说德语。
- Passaporto. - Sprechen sie deutsch.

327
00:47:30,723 --> 00:47:32,224
护照请。
Passport please.

328
00:47:50,493 --> 00:47:52,078
——Nalheim博士?
- Dr. Nalheim?

329
00:48:03,964 --> 00:48:07,093
Kaiser Wilhelm研究所。
Kaiser Wilhelm institute.

330
00:48:12,598 --> 00:48:13,849
谢谢,doktor先生。
Danke, herr doktor.

331
00:48:33,494 --> 00:48:38,249
谢谢。
Danke.

332
00:49:19,498 --> 00:49:21,500
我不是纳尔海姆医生。
I'm not doctor nalheim.

333
00:49:22,251 --> 00:49:27,131
我是美国物理学家，我的名字是——我不在乎你叫什么!
I'm an American physicist and my name is- I don't care what your name is!

334
00:49:27,214 --> 00:49:30,092
-你是美国人!-波达医生，听着。
- You're an American! - Dr. Polda, listen.

335
00:49:30,217 --> 00:49:33,679
我不想听!
I don't want to listen!

336
00:49:33,762 --> 00:49:38,767
你来这里真是疯了。你怎么敢把我置于如此危险的境地。
You're insane to come here. How dare you put me in such danger.

337
00:49:43,939 --> 00:49:47,943
几年前，你给我写了一封信。
A few years ago, you wrote me a letter.

338
00:49:48,027 --> 00:49:54,909
在结尾处你说，“只有服务于全人类的自由科学，才能成为优秀的科学。”
At the end of it you said, "only a free science in the service... Of all humanity can be a good science."

339
00:49:59,413 --> 00:50:02,833
-你是谁?——阿尔瓦Jesper。
- Who are you? - Alvah Jesper.

340
00:50:04,251 --> 00:50:05,461
它是什么?
What is it?

341
00:50:14,637 --> 00:50:15,888
谢谢。
Grazie.

342
00:50:34,573 --> 00:50:35,699
谢谢你！
Thank you.

343
00:50:37,701 --> 00:50:41,664
好吧。我不能背叛我的科学家同事。
All right. I can't betray a fellow scientist.

344
00:50:48,254 --> 00:50:53,759
但你一定是疯了才会来这里。我们没什么可谈的。
But you must be insane to come here. We have nothing to talk over.

345
00:50:53,801 --> 00:50:56,470
什么都没有。
Nothing.

346
00:50:57,680 --> 00:51:00,182
请走吧。
Please go.

347
00:51:00,224 --> 00:51:05,020
-你在研究核裂变。——是明智的。走了。
- You're working on nuclear fission. - Be sensible. Go.

348
00:51:05,104 --> 00:51:09,441
你在为纳粹工作。我知道。
You're working for the Nazis. I know that.

349
00:51:09,525 --> 00:51:11,569
但我不敢相信你愿意这么做。
But I can't believe you're doing it willingly.

350
00:51:11,610 --> 00:51:14,363
哦,心甘情愿,情愿。这有什么关系?
Oh, willingly, unwillingly. What does it matter?

351
00:51:14,446 --> 00:51:18,200
你无权来这里危及我的生命。
You have no right to jeopardise me by coming here.

352
00:51:18,284 --> 00:51:22,454
我有这个权利。卡特琳·洛多给了我权利。
I have the right. Katerin lodor gave me the right.

353
00:51:24,373 --> 00:51:29,336
-你看见卡特琳了?-就在纳粹杀死她之前。
- You saw katerin? - Just before the Nazis killed her.

354
00:51:37,344 --> 00:51:39,847
Katerin,死了。
Katerin, dead.

355
00:51:46,061 --> 00:51:48,689
——Katerin,死了。——被谋杀的。
- Katerin, dead. - Murdered.

356
00:51:50,149 --> 00:51:53,652
她死是因为她不让罪犯利用她的科学知识。
She died because she wouldn't let criminals use her science.

357
00:51:54,028 --> 00:51:57,615
-但你让他们利用了你。-你想要什么?
- But you're letting them use you. - So what do you want?

358
00:51:57,698 --> 00:51:59,950
他们会把我也杀了吗?
That they should murder me too?

359
00:52:00,034 --> 00:52:05,247
——不。但我需要信息。-我要我的生活。
- No. But I want information. - And I want my life.

360
00:52:08,417 --> 00:52:13,380
这是那个从皇家学院辞职而不愿与墨索里尼握手的乔瓦尼·波尔达吗?
Is this the Giovanni polda who resigned from the royal academy... Rather than shake hands with Mussolini?

361
00:52:13,672 --> 00:52:18,093
好吧。我变成了一个懦夫。鄙视我。
All right. I've become a weakling. Despise me.

362
00:52:18,135 --> 00:52:20,763
我不在乎别人。
I don't care about people.

363
00:52:20,846 --> 00:52:24,266
我只关心我自己。只有我自己。
I care about myself. Only myself.

364
00:52:24,350 --> 00:52:28,896
你就是在说谎。这可不是伟大的波尔达人在说话。
You're lying. That's not the great polda talking.

365
00:52:28,979 --> 00:52:32,066
你在害怕什么?他们对你有什么把柄?
What are you afraid of? What hold do they have on you?

366
00:52:32,149 --> 00:52:37,154
把柄?没有把柄。我像空气一样自由。
Hold? No hold. I'm free as air.

367
00:52:37,196 --> 00:52:45,162
他们所拥有的是这个世界上我唯一关心的人，我的女儿玛丽亚。
All they have is the only person in the world I care about, my daughter Maria.

368
00:52:45,245 --> 00:52:49,625
他们抓了她。他的主人和我的主人。
They have her. His masters and mine.

369
00:52:51,794 --> 00:53:01,470
我把他的肖像保存在这里，这样别人就会认为我很爱国。这样我就有东西可恨了。
I keep his portrait here so others will think I'm patriotic... And so I can have something to hate.

370
00:53:03,305 --> 00:53:09,770
自从创世以来，从来没有一个人像我这样憎恨别人。
Not since the beginning of time... Has there been a man who has a hatred like me.

371
00:53:09,853 --> 00:53:15,818
-那就跟他们打。-他们抓了我女儿。
- Then fight them. - They have my daughter.

372
00:53:15,859 --> 00:53:20,072
他们让她每周给我寄一张明信片。
They let her send me a postcard once a week.

373
00:53:20,114 --> 00:53:22,116
我让他们向我讨教。
And I let them pick my brains.

374
00:53:25,828 --> 00:53:29,832
每周，我都会哭一次。
Once a week, I cry.

375
00:53:32,167 --> 00:53:36,338
其他的晚上我喝酒。
The other nights I drink.

376
00:53:37,715 --> 00:53:40,300
现在他们威胁要带她去德国。
Now they threaten to take her into Germany.

377
00:53:40,384 --> 00:53:44,012
我说了一些他们不喜欢的话。只是一件小事。
I said something they didn't like. Only a little thing.

378
00:53:47,599 --> 00:53:50,269
我忘了我自己。
I forgot myself.

379
00:53:50,352 --> 00:53:53,439
你不知道他们也可以带你去德国吗?
Don't you know they can take you into Germany too?

380
00:53:53,480 --> 00:53:56,984
他们被推到这里。你觉得他们撤退后会离开你吗?
They're being pushed back here. You think they'll leave you if they retreat?

381
00:53:57,067 --> 00:54:02,740
不。他们不会离开我的。除非我被榨干了。
No. They won't leave me. Not till I'm squeezed dry.

382
00:54:04,324 --> 00:54:09,079
-但你还是会服侍他们?-他们抓了玛丽亚。
- But still you'll serve them? - They have Maria.

383
00:54:09,121 --> 00:54:11,039
为了她，我愿意为任何人服务。
For her I'll serve anyone.

384
00:54:14,418 --> 00:54:17,129
如果她在另一个国家是安全的呢?
Suppose she were safe in another country?

385
00:54:19,131 --> 00:54:22,801
——什么?-可以的。她在哪里呢?
- What? - It can be done. Where is she?

386
00:54:22,885 --> 00:54:25,846
她被允许在佩鲁贾的一家酒店被看守。
She's permitted to leave under guard in a hotel in perugia.

387
00:54:25,929 --> 00:54:28,932
albergo精益求精。
The albergo excelsior.

388
00:54:29,016 --> 00:54:36,607
让她留在英国吧。美国。给我一个她的笔迹。我们可以做得更好。我们也可以带你出去。
Let her be in england. America. Give me one letter in her handwriting... We can do better than that. We can take you out too.

389
00:54:39,902 --> 00:54:42,780
你不是在和一个又老又病的人玩吧?
You are not playing with an old, sick man?

390
00:54:42,821 --> 00:54:48,035
——没有。-这对她来说很危险，不是吗?
- No. - It will be dangerous for her, won't it?

391
00:54:48,118 --> 00:54:51,163
它可以安排，安全。
It can be arranged, safely.

392
00:54:51,205 --> 00:54:53,248
你可以相信我。
You can trust me.

393
00:54:53,332 --> 00:54:55,918
信任你吗?
Trust you?

394
00:54:57,211 --> 00:55:01,548
我在法西斯主义统治下生活太久了。我不相信任何人。
I've lived too long under fascism. I trust no one.

395
00:55:01,632 --> 00:55:06,762
但我做了一笔生意。如果你帮我，我就帮你。
But a business bargain I make. If you help me, I'll help you.

396
00:55:06,804 --> 00:55:10,474
在那之前，别以为我是个傻瓜。我什么都不会告诉你。
Until then, don't think I'm a fool. I'll tell you nothing.

397
00:55:11,683 --> 00:55:14,144
如果你是这种情况，波尔达医生。
If those are your conditions, Dr. Polda.

398
00:55:14,228 --> 00:55:16,730
是的。
Yes.

399
00:55:19,858 --> 00:55:25,322
照我说的做，也许我又会变成老波尔达了。
Do it, and maybe I'll become the old polda again.

400
00:55:25,405 --> 00:55:29,243
"为人类服务的自由科学"
"A free science in the service of humanity."

401
00:55:29,326 --> 00:55:32,830
“可以是唯一好的科学。”
"Can be the only good science."

402
00:55:35,165 --> 00:55:39,670
现在来。我最好带你经过我的看门狗。
Come now. I'd better take you past my watchdogs.

403
00:56:05,988 --> 00:56:09,449
-再见，教授先生。-再见，纳尔海姆博士。
- Auf wiedersehen, herr professor. - Auf wiedersehen, Dr. Nalheim.

404
00:56:13,954 --> 00:56:15,956
再会。
Auf wiedersehen.

405
00:56:18,834 --> 00:56:19,877
再会。
Auf wiedersehen.

406
00:56:48,280 --> 00:56:50,532
要找到波达的女儿可不是件容易的事。
Getting polda's daughter won't be any cinch.

407
00:56:50,782 --> 00:56:52,034
我们该怎么做呢?
How do we go about it?

408
00:56:53,619 --> 00:56:58,832
-我和他会处理的。你待着别动。-我也许能你也许能让我们陷入困境。这是所有。
- He and I will go about it. You stay put. - I might be able You might be able to land us in the soup. That's all.

409
00:56:59,333 --> 00:57:02,336
你能在意大利闲逛多久不碰上盖世太保?
How long can you wander around Italy without running into the gestapo?

410
00:57:02,419 --> 00:57:03,670
或者是ovra ?
Or the ovra?

411
00:57:04,630 --> 00:57:07,382
你以为他们不会跟柏林核实你的文件吗?
You think they won't check your papers with Berlin?

412
00:57:07,466 --> 00:57:10,719
不，先生，你待着别动，否则交易取消。
No, sir. You stay put or the deal is off.

413
00:57:12,054 --> 00:57:14,056
好吧。我可以住在哪里?
Okay. Where can I stay?

414
00:57:19,186 --> 00:57:21,605
-你有食品券吗?——是的。
- Do you have any food stamps? - Yes.

415
00:57:22,689 --> 00:57:23,941
那这就是最好的地方。
Then this is the best place.

416
00:57:25,108 --> 00:57:28,320
别让人看见，等着。
Just keep out of sight, and wait.

417
00:57:36,203 --> 00:57:48,799
……如果我们抓到波尔达的女儿，我就在报纸上发布雷纳尔多·阿马迪中尉的死讯。
If... If we get polda's daughter, I'll put a notice in the papers announcing the death in action... Of lieutenant- lieutenant rinaldo amadi.

418
00:57:48,882 --> 00:57:54,137
——Amadi ?——嗯。A-m-a-d-i。Amadi。
- Amadi? - Mm-hmm. A-m-a-d-i. Amadi.

419
00:57:54,179 --> 00:57:58,016
当你看到它的时候，去罗莫利，波尔达的牙医。
When you see it, go to romoli's, polda's dentist.

420
00:57:58,100 --> 00:58:01,144
他会让教授去找你的。
He'll have the professor there for you.

421
00:58:01,186 --> 00:58:04,356
在北部有游击队的飞机场。我们将乘飞机去。
There are partisan airfields in the north. We'll go out by plane.

422
00:58:05,816 --> 00:58:07,734
-你知道葡萄园吗，皮纳罗?——是的。
- You know the vineyard, pinaro's? - Yes.

423
00:58:07,818 --> 00:58:09,987
采取polda那里。
Take polda there.

424
00:58:11,822 --> 00:58:15,242
-你可能要多久?-需要多久就多久。
- How long are you likely to be? - As long as it takes.

425
00:58:15,283 --> 00:58:18,954
-大概一周吧。-如果你找不到玛丽亚怎么办?
- A week maybe. - What if you don't get Maria?

426
00:58:19,037 --> 00:58:21,790
如果我们完全没收到你的消息怎么办?
What if we don't hear from you at all?

427
00:58:21,873 --> 00:58:24,626
战争的命运，艾。那你就只能靠自己了。
The fortunes of war, ai. You'll be on your own then.

428
00:58:24,710 --> 00:58:27,796
这是你的外套。
Here's your coat.

429
00:58:27,838 --> 00:58:30,007
谢谢你！谢谢。
Thank you. Grazie.

430
00:58:32,801 --> 00:58:36,638
-就像新的一样。——Marsoli。Andiamo。
- It's just like new. - Marsoli. Andiamo.

431
00:58:40,058 --> 00:58:43,520
——祝你好运。-吉娜，你能到外面看看吗?
- Good luck. - Gina, will you look outside please?

432
00:59:02,748 --> 00:59:05,000
没关系。
It's all right.

433
00:59:12,174 --> 00:59:15,343
吉娜,再见。
Gina, arrivederci.

434
00:59:16,678 --> 00:59:20,015
——再见。-我会再见你的。
- Arrivederci. - I'll be seeing you.

435
00:59:48,877 --> 00:59:52,130
好吧，别客气。
Well, make yourself at home.

436
00:59:52,172 --> 00:59:54,091
谢谢。
Thanks.

437
01:00:02,599 --> 01:00:05,685
我想让我在你手上比你想的要多。
I guess having me here on your hands was more than you bargained for.

438
01:00:06,061 --> 01:00:09,356
在工作中，我们取其所来。
In our work we take what comes.

439
01:00:13,902 --> 01:00:16,196
请不要再打量我了。
Please stop looking me over.

440
01:00:17,531 --> 01:00:19,533
你长得很好看。
You're nice to look at.

441
01:00:22,536 --> 01:00:25,413
我们就像歌剧中的一幕。
Just like a scene in the opera, we are.

442
01:00:25,455 --> 01:00:28,959
百姓去。留下这对年轻夫妇独自一人。
The people go. The young couple is left alone.

443
01:00:29,042 --> 01:00:33,171
快，这个年轻人一定要说些恭维话。这是预期。
Quick, the young man must make compliments. It's expected.

444
01:00:33,213 --> 01:00:37,592
只是这里没有音乐，你也不是男高音。
Only there isn't any music, and you are not a tenor.

445
01:00:37,634 --> 01:00:42,347
有你自己的方式，但在你了解我之前不要加我。
Have it your own way, but don't add me up before you know me.

446
01:00:49,729 --> 01:00:51,773
我们要听一整晚吗?
Are we gonna have to listen to that all night?

447
01:00:51,815 --> 01:00:54,901
也许你可以问问猫。
Maybe you ask the cat.

448
01:00:54,985 --> 01:00:57,070
你满脑子都是醋，不是吗?
You're full of vinegar, aren't you?

449
01:00:58,989 --> 01:01:00,907
这听起来饿了。
It sounds hungry.

450
01:01:00,991 --> 01:01:03,785
如果人们饿了，只有猫才会饿。
Well, if people are hungry, it's only natural cats should be.

451
01:01:05,370 --> 01:01:06,872
你有牛奶吗?
Have you got any milk for it?

452
01:01:08,748 --> 01:01:11,084
牛奶吗?哦,我记得。
Milk? Oh, I remember.

453
01:01:11,126 --> 01:01:13,211
它来自奶牛，不是吗?
It comes from cows, no?

454
01:01:13,295 --> 01:01:15,422
好的婴儿。
Good for babies.

455
01:01:17,549 --> 01:01:20,927
不过，我还是讨厌听到猫哭。也许来块面包。
Still, I hate to hear a cat cry. Maybe a piece of bread.

456
01:01:21,011 --> 01:01:23,930
美国人喜欢猫，嗯?
The American likes cats, hmm?

457
01:01:24,014 --> 01:01:27,642
只是你现在在欧洲。在这里，你可以在肉店里找到猫。
Only you're in Europe now. Here you find cats in butcher shops.

458
01:01:27,726 --> 01:01:33,190
这是幸运的。但也许明天，就会掉进别人的炖锅里。
This one's been lucky. But by tomorrow maybe, plop into somebody's stew pot.

459
01:01:33,273 --> 01:01:38,612
生活在一个不仅喂猫，而且还喂孩子的国家一定很好。
It must be nice to live in a country where not only cats are fed, but children.

460
01:01:39,696 --> 01:01:43,408
拜托，我要去穿睡衣了。
Please, I'm going to put on my nightgown.

461
01:01:54,628 --> 01:01:57,756
像你这样的女孩是怎么习惯这种生活的?
How does a girl like you get used to this kind of life?

462
01:01:57,839 --> 01:02:00,508
你觉得会有人习惯吗?
Do you think anyone gets used to it?

463
01:02:00,550 --> 01:02:03,094
我觉得你做得很好，吉娜。
I think you do wonderfully, Gina.

464
01:02:03,178 --> 01:02:06,097
我从没见过这么有勇气的女孩。
I never knew a girl with so much courage.

465
01:02:06,181 --> 01:02:08,183
勇气?
Courage?

466
01:02:10,018 --> 01:02:12,854
你是个成年人，知道的那么少。
You're a grown-up man and know so little.

467
01:02:12,938 --> 01:02:18,109
你不懂猫，也不懂人。-你怎么了，吉娜?
You know nothing about cats, - and nothing about people. - What's the matter with you, Gina?

468
01:02:18,193 --> 01:02:21,112
哦，没关系，只不过你是从月球来的。
Oh, no matter, except you come from the moon.

469
01:02:21,196 --> 01:02:24,658
而我们却像拉撒路一样生活。
And here we live like, like Lazarus.

470
01:02:24,741 --> 01:02:28,870
我们躺在坟墓里等待救世主的到来。
We lie in the grave waiting for the saviour to come.

471
01:02:30,038 --> 01:02:34,542
不过我不是从月球来的，像你这样的意大利人也不是随便躺着的。
Only I don't come from the moon, and Italians like you aren't just lying down.

472
01:02:47,389 --> 01:02:49,975
你坐沙发太长了。你睡那张床。
You're too long for the couch. You take the bed.

473
01:02:50,016 --> 01:02:52,769
——唔唔。在这项工作中，我们是同志。
- Mm-mmm. - In this work we're comrades.

474
01:02:52,811 --> 01:02:56,606
——没有。-明天你的背就要断了。我希望。
- No. - Tomorrow you'll have a broken back. I hope.

475
01:02:56,690 --> 01:02:58,692
谢谢。
Thanks.

476
01:03:32,559 --> 01:03:34,686
嘿。
Hey.

477
01:03:34,728 --> 01:03:36,730
谢谢你！
Thank you.

478
01:03:48,533 --> 01:03:50,618
我再也听不到那只猫的声音了。
I don't hear that cat anymore.

479
01:03:50,660 --> 01:03:55,248
在这个国家，连猫都知道哭是没有用的。
In this country even the cats learn it's no use to cry.

480
01:04:19,481 --> 01:04:22,859
米迦，米迦，米迦，米迦，米迦。
Micha, micha, micha, micha, micha.

481
01:04:29,240 --> 01:04:32,452
我希望她身上有跳蚤。
Here, I hope she has fleas.

482
01:04:39,417 --> 01:04:41,669
对不起，我没有洋葱肝。
Excuse me, I have no liver with onions.

483
01:04:41,753 --> 01:04:43,797
只有剩菜。
Only leftovers.

484
01:04:43,838 --> 01:04:48,051
现在闭嘴，让我睡觉，否则我就把你扔出窗外。
Now you shut up and let me sleep, or I'll throw you right out the window.

485
01:04:56,309 --> 01:05:00,688
晚安，各位。
Good night.

486
01:05:05,568 --> 01:05:07,028
人工智能?
Ai?

487
01:05:07,112 --> 01:05:08,113
是吗?
Yes?

488
01:05:14,119 --> 01:05:15,912
我说的不全是真的。
I don't mean all I say.

489
01:05:19,165 --> 01:05:21,167
我知道你不知道。
I know you don't.

490
01:05:22,460 --> 01:05:24,421
晚安，各位。
Good night.

491
01:05:24,504 --> 01:05:26,506
晚安，各位。
Good night.

492
01:05:41,563 --> 01:05:42,564
不!
No!

493
01:05:48,361 --> 01:05:49,362
吉娜。
Gina.

494
01:05:51,114 --> 01:05:52,407
吉娜!
Gina!

495
01:05:56,578 --> 01:05:59,914
不要担心。一切都是好的。
Don't be worried. Everything's all right.

496
01:06:00,999 --> 01:06:03,168
哎，你为什么要叫醒我?
Ai, why do you wake me?

497
01:06:03,251 --> 01:06:06,880
-为什么要这样吓唬我?-你在做梦。
- Why frighten me like this? - You were dreaming.

498
01:06:06,963 --> 01:06:09,716
你在睡梦中哭泣。
You were crying in your sleep.

499
01:06:11,843 --> 01:06:13,928
哦,是的。
Oh, yes.

500
01:06:13,970 --> 01:06:16,556
我记得。
I remember.

501
01:06:17,640 --> 01:06:19,601
哦。
Oh.

502
01:06:20,685 --> 01:06:22,729
告诉我可能会有帮助。
It might help to tell me about it.

503
01:06:26,107 --> 01:06:31,529
你在散兵坑里战斗很久了，不是吗，吉娜?
You've been fighting in the foxholes a long time, haven't you, Gina?

504
01:06:31,613 --> 01:06:47,921
今晚，我对自己说，现在，也许，也许，一整个星期，一切都会变得容易。
Tonight I, I say to myself, now maybe, maybe for, for a whole week, it'll be easy.

505
01:06:47,962 --> 01:06:50,965
待在房间里。
Stay in the room.

506
01:06:51,049 --> 01:06:53,426
唱歌一点。
Sing a little.

507
01:06:53,468 --> 01:06:57,847
灰尘洗碗。
Dust wash dishes.

508
01:06:57,931 --> 01:07:01,142
不。不容易的。
No. Not easy.

509
01:07:03,770 --> 01:07:06,606
即使是在睡觉的时候。
Not even in sleep.

510
01:07:25,500 --> 01:07:27,919
夫人多米尼克?
Signora Dominica?

511
01:07:42,308 --> 01:07:44,352
它是什么?
What is it?

512
01:07:44,435 --> 01:07:46,938
Si。
Si.

513
01:07:46,980 --> 01:07:48,982
他的猫。他想要他的猫。
His cat. He wants his cat.

514
01:07:49,023 --> 01:07:53,194
在那里。快。
Over there. Quick.

515
01:07:59,993 --> 01:08:04,163
谢谢,小姐,谢谢。
Grazie, signorina, grazie.

516
01:08:17,093 --> 01:08:20,179
不，不是意大利人。
No, non parlo italiano.

517
01:08:20,221 --> 01:08:25,476
哦,congratulazioni,夫人。Congratulazioni。
Oh, congratulazioni, signori. Congratulazioni.

518
01:08:34,152 --> 01:08:38,281
哦,是的。
Oh, si.

519
01:08:43,578 --> 01:08:46,623
Buona命运,夫人。Buona命运,夫人
Buona fortuna, signore. Buona fortuna, signore

520
01:08:48,958 --> 01:08:51,085
布拉瓦。Bravissima。
brava. Bravissima.

521
01:08:51,169 --> 01:08:55,423
那只猫。肯定是猫。
The cat. It had to be the cat.

522
01:08:55,506 --> 01:09:04,223
总是一些小事，一些我们无法计划的事情让我们最终落入警察手中。
It's always the little things, the things we can't plan that make us end up in the hands of the police.

523
01:09:06,934 --> 01:09:10,021
-我们不能再呆在这里了。——为什么?
- We can't stay here any longer. - Why?

524
01:09:10,104 --> 01:09:12,023
-他是特工吗?——没有。
- Is he an agent? - No.

525
01:09:12,106 --> 01:09:15,652
但每个看门人都得报告家里有新来者。
But every janitor has to report any new person in the house.

526
01:09:17,028 --> 01:09:20,782
我告诉他你是我丈夫。
I told him you're my husband.

527
01:09:22,367 --> 01:09:24,285
你为什么这么做?
Why did you do that?

528
01:09:24,369 --> 01:09:26,579
我不能去警局登记。
I can't register with the police.

529
01:09:26,621 --> 01:09:30,833
-我们不能冒这个险——我知道。我犯了个错误。
- We can't risk that. - I know. I made a mistake.

530
01:09:35,171 --> 01:09:39,092
-你知道其他安全屋吗?-我在思考。
- Do you know any other safe house? - I'm trying to think.

531
01:09:39,175 --> 01:09:42,095
我们不能没日没夜地在街上走。我们肯定会被接走的。
We can't walk the streets day and night. We'd be picked up sure.

532
01:09:42,178 --> 01:09:45,765
我知道。闭嘴，让我想想。
I know. Shut up for a minute, and let me think.

533
01:09:47,392 --> 01:09:50,645
我们在这里完成。
We're finished here.

534
01:09:50,728 --> 01:09:54,023
-这不是你的错。-我没必要说你是我丈夫。
- It's not your fault. - I didn't have to say you're my husband.

535
01:09:54,107 --> 01:09:56,818
在我们的工作中没有那种骄傲的空间。
In our work there's no room for that sort of pride.

536
01:09:56,859 --> 01:10:02,532
没有自尊，你就不会是吉娜，不要为你的自尊感到羞愧。
Without pride you wouldn't be Gina don't be ashamed of your pride.

537
01:10:04,325 --> 01:10:10,998
昨晚，而现在，你说的话让我在这里感觉轻松多了。
Last night, and now, you say things that make me feel easier in here.

538
01:10:12,917 --> 01:10:15,378
也许你觉得自己很仁慈。
Maybe you feel charity.

539
01:10:15,461 --> 01:10:20,425
或者，你喜欢人?
Or maybe, you like people?

540
01:10:20,466 --> 01:10:22,635
我喜欢猫。
Mostly I like cats.

541
01:10:32,812 --> 01:10:35,064
这张照片是什么时候拍的，吉娜?
When was this picture taken, Gina?

542
01:10:39,152 --> 01:10:41,362
就在战争之前。
Just before the war.

543
01:10:43,740 --> 01:10:45,908
一百年前。
A hundred years ago.

544
01:11:10,057 --> 01:11:11,976
运气吗?
Any luck?

545
01:11:12,018 --> 01:11:16,898
一套公寓。两间房和一间浴室，住三天。
An apartment. Two rooms and a bath for three days.

546
01:11:16,981 --> 01:11:20,443
——洗澡?是谁给了我们这些?-我曾经认识的一位女教师。
- A bath? Who's giving us all that? - A schoolmistress I once knew.

547
01:11:20,526 --> 01:11:22,445
法西斯党员。
A fascist party member.

548
01:11:22,528 --> 01:11:28,826
我告诉她我有一个德国朋友，非常重要，她非常以我为荣。
I told her I had a German friend who was very important, and she was very proud of me.

549
01:11:28,910 --> 01:11:30,995
累了,吉娜吗?
Tired, Gina?

550
01:11:31,078 --> 01:11:33,998
- - - - - -不坏。饿了吗?——嗯。
- Not bad. Hungry? - Hmm.

551
01:11:35,291 --> 01:11:37,293
不,谢谢。
No, thanks.

552
01:11:38,586 --> 01:11:41,422
苹果含有大量的能量。
There's a lot of energy in an apple.

553
01:11:51,057 --> 01:11:53,100
那是什么?
What's that?

554
01:11:55,520 --> 01:11:57,939
我一直在忙着等你呢。
Oh, I was trying to keep busy waiting for you.

555
01:11:58,064 --> 01:12:00,983
但它是什么呢?
But what is it?

556
01:12:01,067 --> 01:12:04,821
这叫做画正弦波的线积分。
It's called plotting the line integral of a sine wave.

557
01:12:04,862 --> 01:12:07,198
哦，这并不像听起来那么难。
Oh, it's not as difficult as it sounds.

558
01:12:09,200 --> 01:12:17,124
我想象着我正骑着其中的一匹马，试着算出我总共能走多远，同时上上下下。
I was imagining I was riding one of those horses, trying to figure out how far I would go altogether, going around and up and down at the same time.

559
01:12:20,711 --> 01:12:23,339
上上下下的马。
Horses going up and down.

560
01:12:23,381 --> 01:12:25,299
和孩子,音乐。
And kids, music.

561
01:12:29,428 --> 01:12:31,639
-你来过这里吗，吉娜?——嗯。
- Ever come here, Gina? - Mm-hmm.

562
01:12:32,974 --> 01:12:34,433
在战争之前。
Before the war.

563
01:12:35,852 --> 01:12:39,772
音乐一直在播放“giovinezza”，一首法西斯歌曲。
The music played "giovinezza" all the time, a fascist song.

564
01:12:39,856 --> 01:12:41,482
它破坏了我的兴致。
It spoiled it for me.

565
01:12:43,526 --> 01:12:47,572
-你带着个男孩来?-是的。
- You come here with a boy? - Yeah.

566
01:12:47,613 --> 01:12:49,824
你喜欢的那个?
One you liked?

567
01:12:49,866 --> 01:12:53,619
他和我一起拍的照片。他演奏大提琴。
He was in the picture with me. He played the cello.

568
01:12:53,703 --> 01:12:56,247
他现在在哪里?
Where is he now?

569
01:12:56,289 --> 01:12:59,166
在某处。如果没有他的大提琴。
Somewhere. Without his cello.

570
01:13:03,880 --> 01:13:05,965
也许战争结束后，我可能会回来。
Maybe after the war, I might come back.

571
01:13:11,053 --> 01:13:14,307
我会带你来这里。但音乐会有所不同。
And I'd bring you here. But the music would be different.

572
01:13:16,350 --> 01:13:19,270
战后会有很大的不同。
After the war a lot will be different.

573
01:13:20,980 --> 01:13:23,232
但你不会回来了。
But you won't come back.

574
01:13:23,274 --> 01:13:25,568
我可能会。为什么不呢?
I might. Why not?

575
01:13:29,530 --> 01:13:31,282
现在的时间。我们可以去。
It's time now. We can go.

576
01:14:05,149 --> 01:14:08,486
——哇。-今晚我是战前吉娜。
- Whoa. - Tonight I am pre-war Gina.

577
01:14:13,157 --> 01:14:15,493
我在学校教我的小孩。
I teach my little children in school.

578
01:14:17,912 --> 01:14:20,623
星期三我演奏室内乐。
Wednesday I play chamber music.

579
01:14:24,543 --> 01:14:26,671
我很无辜的。
I'm very innocent.

580
01:14:30,800 --> 01:14:32,718
我很容易脸红。
And I'm easy to blush.

581
01:14:36,180 --> 01:14:39,433
-换一套衣服就可以了吗?-我们走着瞧吧。
- A change of clothes does all that? - Well, we'll see.

582
01:14:48,109 --> 01:14:50,945
我还是很漂亮，不是吗?
I'm still pretty, no?

583
01:14:52,738 --> 01:14:55,074
嗯，有一点。
Hmm, a little bit.

584
01:14:56,617 --> 01:15:02,873
即使你不这么认为，我遇到的所有男人，他们都说我很漂亮。
Well, even if you don't think so, all the ovra men I meet, they tell me I'm pretty.

585
01:15:10,798 --> 01:15:28,983
我认识一个人他长得又高又高，他移动着他的身体，像一颗炮弹，再见吧，亲爱的，再见吧。
I know a man he is long and tall, he moves his body, like a cannonball, fare thee well, my honey, fare thee well.

586
01:15:29,066 --> 01:15:31,819
——那是什么?-一首美国牛仔歌曲。
- What's that? - An American cowboy song.

587
01:15:35,698 --> 01:15:40,411
别那么滑稽。你从新亚利桑那州飞来的一架飞机教我的。
Don't look so funny. One of your shot-down fliers from new Arizona taught it to me.

588
01:15:41,704 --> 01:15:44,915
——新墨西哥州。——新亚利桑那州。
- New Mexico. - New Arizona.

589
01:15:44,999 --> 01:15:47,626
好的,新的亚利桑那州。
Okay, new Arizona.

590
01:15:47,710 --> 01:15:50,296
他教我的。
He taught it to me.

591
01:15:50,337 --> 01:15:52,923
其余的我都不知道。
The rest I never learned.

592
01:15:52,965 --> 01:15:55,384
只有第一行。
Only the first lines.

593
01:15:55,426 --> 01:15:57,511
他非常的不错。
He was nice.

594
01:15:57,595 --> 01:15:59,680
现在。
Now.

595
01:16:01,432 --> 01:16:03,392
我看起来怎么样?
How do I look?

596
01:16:05,144 --> 01:16:07,396
——战前。-你是说真的吗?
- Pre-war. - Do you mean it?

597
01:16:07,480 --> 01:16:10,149
我当然知道。
Of course I do.

598
01:16:10,232 --> 01:16:12,318
我不是奥夫拉人。
I'm no ovra man.

599
01:16:12,359 --> 01:16:16,322
-你为什么这么说?-是你提出来的
- Why do you say that? - You brought it up.

600
01:16:16,405 --> 01:16:19,825
哦。我猜你是嫉妒了。嗯?
Oh. You're jealous, I suppose. Hmm?

601
01:16:19,867 --> 01:16:22,787
你觉得我就不能吃醋吗?
Do you think I couldn't be jealous?

602
01:16:22,828 --> 01:16:25,331
你想让我跳舞吗?
Do you want me to dance?

603
01:16:36,926 --> 01:16:39,512
也许我是嫉妒，吉娜
Maybe I am jealous, Gina

604
01:16:49,939 --> 01:16:54,693
不，别跟我做爱。不要成为我喜欢的人。
No, don't make love to me. Don't be somebody I like.

605
01:16:54,735 --> 01:16:59,365
如果你想吻我，我也想吻你，那我们就吻吧。
If you feel like kissing me, and I feel like kissing you, so we kiss.

606
01:16:59,448 --> 01:17:01,700
但是不要太认真。
But don't be serious.

607
01:17:01,784 --> 01:17:05,204
在我的工作中，我亲吻时没有感觉。
In my job, I kiss without feeling.

608
01:17:05,287 --> 01:17:08,666
上周，一个留着傻胡子的男人。
Last week, an ovra man with a silly moustache.

609
01:17:08,707 --> 01:17:12,419
下个星期，是一头盖世太保肥猪。
Next week, a fat, gestapo pig.

610
01:17:19,176 --> 01:17:20,469
吉娜。
Gina.

611
01:17:21,846 --> 01:17:23,764
吉娜,女孩。
Gina, girl.

612
01:17:23,848 --> 01:17:26,767
你为什么一直抽自己，吉娜?
Why do you keep whipping yourself, Gina?

613
01:17:31,689 --> 01:17:37,945
你觉得，你觉得在地下当个信使好吗?
Do you think, you think it's good, to be a courier in the underground?

614
01:17:37,987 --> 01:17:41,574
你觉得这很刺激，很英勇。
You think it's exciting, heroic.

615
01:17:43,659 --> 01:17:47,496
不。如果你和人渣斗争，你就会变成人渣。这是所有。
No. If you fight scum, you become scum. That's all.

616
01:17:47,538 --> 01:17:50,499
不。我知道你是什么人。
No. I know what you are.

617
01:17:52,251 --> 01:17:54,295
离照片上的小女孩不远。
Not so far from that little girl in the picture.

618
01:18:01,510 --> 01:18:03,721
到门口去。
Go to the door.

619
01:18:13,606 --> 01:18:15,941
-再见，夫人。,晚上好。
- Buona sera, signora. - Buona sera.

620
01:18:21,572 --> 01:18:23,115
呃,联合国的纪念品。
Uh, UN momento.

621
01:18:32,541 --> 01:18:34,543
谢谢。
Grazie.

622
01:18:42,551 --> 01:18:48,265
-是谁?-两姐妹为战争中的孤儿募捐。
- Who was it? - Two sisters collecting charity, for children orphaned by the war.

623
01:18:48,766 --> 01:18:51,352
-这有什么不对吗?——好吧,等待。
- Anything wrong with that? - Well, wait.

624
01:19:11,789 --> 01:19:13,207
我们得离开这里。
We've got to get out of here.

625
01:19:13,582 --> 01:19:16,168
-她们不是真正的姐妹。-你怎么知道?
- They're not real sisters. - How do you know?

626
01:19:16,543 --> 01:19:19,880
他们停在街角的一辆汽车旁。
They're stopping at an automobile parked on the corner.

627
01:19:19,964 --> 01:19:21,799
-我们被监视了。来吧。-让我看看。
- We're being watched. Come on. - Let me see.

628
01:19:21,882 --> 01:19:23,759
-离那扇窗户远点。-等一下。
- Stay away from that window. - Wait a minute.

629
01:19:23,842 --> 01:19:27,554
我跟着感觉走。我内心很害怕，我要对你负责。
I follow my feelings. I feel scared inside, and I'm responsible for you.

630
01:19:27,596 --> 01:19:31,183
-相信我的感觉。-我们不要太紧张了。
- Trust my feelings. - Let's not get too jumpy about this.

631
01:19:31,225 --> 01:19:33,769
如果他们是警察，我们早就被捕了。
If they're from the police, we'd be arrested already.

632
01:19:33,852 --> 01:19:37,731
我知道有什么不对劲。我比你有更多的经验。
I know there's something wrong. I have more experience than you have.

633
01:19:37,773 --> 01:19:43,654
-我们必须马上离开这里。-好吧，吉娜，随你便。
- We must get out of here and quick. - All right, Gina have it your way.

634
01:19:49,326 --> 01:19:52,037
我们今晚在这里很安全。
Here we'll be safe for the night.

635
01:20:12,016 --> 01:20:17,813
我认为这是安全的。然后明天天一亮，我们就搬走。
I think this is safe. Then tomorrow, as soon as it gets light, we'll move.

636
01:20:17,896 --> 01:20:19,898
好吧。
All right.

637
01:20:33,829 --> 01:20:37,249
作为一栋被监视的房子，我们很容易就逃了出来。
For a house that was being watched, we got out awfully easy.

638
01:20:37,291 --> 01:20:39,918
我相信我的感觉。
I trust my feelings.

639
01:20:42,463 --> 01:20:43,714
我颤抖。
I'm shaking.

640
01:20:44,214 --> 01:20:45,924
我浑身发抖。
I'm shaking all over.

641
01:20:48,886 --> 01:20:56,018
你会崩溃的，吉娜你每天都会崩溃一点。
Now you'll go to pieces, Gina every day you fall apart a little more.

642
01:20:57,436 --> 01:21:00,064
太长了。太多了。
Too long. Too much.

643
01:21:00,147 --> 01:21:03,233
太多的担心，太多的恐惧。
Too much worry and too much fright.

644
01:21:05,903 --> 01:21:07,821
太多的死亡。
Too much death.

645
01:21:07,905 --> 01:21:12,201
吉娜，你会没事的。
Gina, you're going to be all right.

646
01:21:12,284 --> 01:21:14,286
别担心。
Don't worry.

647
01:21:18,332 --> 01:21:20,667
我希望你喜欢我。
I want you to like me.

648
01:21:20,751 --> 01:21:23,337
我想让你嫉妒我。
I want you to be jealous over me.

649
01:21:23,420 --> 01:21:30,594
我想让你以为我是一个从没被吻过的穿白裙子的女孩。
I want you to think I'm a girl in a white dress... Who has never been kissed before.

650
01:22:01,333 --> 01:22:05,003
广告上登了。
It's in. The advertisement.

651
01:22:06,797 --> 01:22:09,466
——在哪里?——在这里。
- Where? - Here.

652
01:22:09,508 --> 01:22:12,052
“莱amadi中尉。”
"Lieutenant rinaldo amadi."

653
01:22:12,136 --> 01:22:14,138
他们把波尔达的女儿救出来了。
They've got polda's daughter out.

654
01:22:14,179 --> 01:22:16,765
现在我们必须去罗摩里餐厅。
Now we must go to romoli's.

655
01:22:16,849 --> 01:22:20,227
-噩梦结束了，宝贝。-另一个开始，把polda弄出来。
- Nightmare's over, baby. - Another one starts, to get polda out.

656
01:22:20,269 --> 01:22:24,565
——我们将管理。你给我买剃须刀了吗?——是的。
- We'll manage. Did you get me a razor? - Yes.

657
01:22:24,648 --> 01:22:32,573
剃刀，刀片，还有……一块肥皂。
Razor, and a blade, and... a piece of soap.

658
01:22:33,949 --> 01:22:35,951
谢谢。
Thanks.

659
01:22:41,373 --> 01:22:43,333
不客气
You're welcome.

660
01:22:45,043 --> 01:22:53,218
哎，在我们的工作中，你遇到一个男人或一个女人，一天或一个星期，然后再见。
Ai, in our work you meet a man or a woman, for a day or a week, then good-bye.

661
01:22:53,302 --> 01:22:56,638
但有一天，我的心离我很近。
But in one day heart's come close.

662
01:22:56,722 --> 01:23:04,396
也许在和平时期我甚至都不看你，说"愚蠢的美国游客"
Maybe in peacetime I don't even look at you, say, "silly American tourist."

663
01:23:04,480 --> 01:23:12,196
但现在我告诉你，我很喜欢这个长长的美国人，我想让你知道。
But now I tell you, I like very much this long American, and I want you to know.

664
01:23:12,237 --> 01:23:15,616
为什么只有“喜欢”，吉娜?
Why only "like," Gina?

665
01:23:15,699 --> 01:23:18,118
这样更好，更简单。
It's better. Easier.

666
01:23:18,160 --> 01:23:20,913
为什么?
Why?

667
01:23:20,954 --> 01:23:25,042
有时候它是更好的。
Sometimes it's better.

668
01:23:26,627 --> 01:23:31,089
哎哟!你得刮胡子了，快点儿。
Ouch! You must shave, and hurry.

669
01:23:31,173 --> 01:23:33,383
我们得去罗摩利餐厅
We've got to go to romoli's

670
01:25:01,972 --> 01:25:04,016
把你的外套给我。
Give me your coat.

671
01:25:04,057 --> 01:25:05,934
把这个。
Take this.

672
01:25:34,463 --> 01:25:36,882
从门口进去。
Get into that doorway.

673
01:27:13,061 --> 01:27:15,063
吉娜,polda !
Gina, get polda!

674
01:28:41,942 --> 01:28:45,403
听着，这就像杀死一条疯狗。
Look, it's just like killing a mad dog.

675
01:28:45,487 --> 01:28:49,241
除了狗，你可以感到抱歉。他生病不是他的错。
Except for the dog you can feel sorry. It's not his fault he is sick.

676
01:29:19,896 --> 01:29:25,610
Jesper医生，Jesper医生，什么事?
Dr.jesper - Dr. Jesper - yes?

677
01:29:25,652 --> 01:29:28,363
我想你最好开车。
I think you'd better drive.

678
01:29:28,446 --> 01:29:30,740
哦，没什么严重的。
Oh, it's nothing serious.

679
01:29:30,824 --> 01:29:33,952
我这个年纪有点太兴奋了。
Just a little too much excitement at my age.

680
01:29:34,035 --> 01:29:38,498
我一见到玛丽亚就会好的。
I'll be again all right as soon as I've seen Maria.

681
01:29:38,582 --> 01:29:41,084
好吧。拐弯处停车。
All right. Stop around the bend.

682
01:30:20,624 --> 01:30:22,626
Jesper
Jesper

683
01:30:29,507 --> 01:30:32,594
这是我第一次听到你的名字。
That's the first time I heard your name.

684
01:30:38,266 --> 01:30:42,812
Jesper，我喜欢。
Jesper I like it.

685
01:31:13,635 --> 01:31:16,096
谢谢你！
Thank you.

686
01:31:24,187 --> 01:31:26,314
小指中尉愿为您效劳。
Lieutenant pinkie at your service.

687
01:31:26,356 --> 01:31:28,566
——小手指。-请进，伙计们。
- Pinkie. - Come on in, folks.

688
01:31:30,026 --> 01:31:32,529
没关系。小指。
It's okay. It's pinkie.

689
01:31:34,280 --> 01:31:36,533
——嗨,ai。——小手指。
- Hi, ai. - Pinkie.

690
01:31:36,574 --> 01:31:39,160
-认识一下波尔达教授。-你好，波达教授?
- Meet professor polda. - How do you do, professor polda?

691
01:31:39,244 --> 01:31:41,496
-你好。-你从哪弄来的?
- How do you do. - Where'd you get that stuff?

692
01:31:41,538 --> 01:31:44,958
哦,这个吗?我的旅行服装。
Oh, this? My traveling costume.

693
01:31:45,041 --> 01:31:47,085
挺合身的，不是吗?
Kind of a nice fit, isn't it?

694
01:31:47,127 --> 01:31:49,212
哦,pinaro见面。
Oh, meet pinaro.

695
01:31:49,254 --> 01:31:53,508
伟大的老家伙。如果他穿着制服，他会有满满一箱水果沙拉。
Great old guy. If he were in uniform he'd have a chest full of fruit salad.

696
01:31:53,591 --> 01:31:57,470
——Pinaro。——Benvenuti。
- Pinaro. - Benvenuti.

697
01:31:57,512 --> 01:31:59,514
让我们进去。
Let's go in.

698
01:32:01,349 --> 01:32:04,602
-这位是彼得罗-祝你好运，彼得罗。
- And, uh, this is Pietro. - Buona sera, Pietro.

699
01:32:10,567 --> 01:32:12,610
——marsoli在哪?-他马上就来。
- Where's marsoli? - He'll be along any minute.

700
01:32:12,694 --> 01:32:14,779
和波达小姐。
And with signorina polda.

701
01:32:14,821 --> 01:32:17,657
-她安全吗?——绝对安全。
- Is she safe? - Perfectly safe.

702
01:32:17,741 --> 01:32:20,326
很高兴她能再见到你。
And very happy she's going to see you again.

703
01:32:20,368 --> 01:32:24,372
-遇到麻烦了吗?-整个行动都很顺利。
- Run into any trouble? - Not a hitch in the whole operation.

704
01:32:24,456 --> 01:32:28,084
像一阵风。我们通过酒店里的一个小女孩解决的。
Went like a breeze. We worked it through a little girl in the hotel.

705
01:32:28,168 --> 01:32:32,547
漂亮的孩子。一开始有点害怕，但我打动了她善良的本性。
Nice kid. A little scared at first, but I appealed to her better nature.

706
01:32:35,341 --> 01:32:40,597
我们的秘鲁朋友整理了一些文件，这样就可以坐火车旅行了。——谢谢。
Our perugian friends fixed up some papers - that made it okay to travel by train. - Thank you.

707
01:32:40,680 --> 01:32:42,974
今天下午我们在最近的城镇下了车。
This afternoon we got off at the nearest town.

708
01:32:43,016 --> 01:32:45,560
我想其他人会让天黑后这里更容易。
I figured the others would make it easier here after dark.

709
01:32:45,602 --> 01:32:49,647
所以我走在前面，检查了一下我们预定的行程。
So I came on ahead and checked on our reservations for the trip out.

710
01:32:49,731 --> 01:32:52,400
——哦,pinaro。-我们在哪里和飞机会合?
- Oh, pinaro. - Where do we meet the plane?

711
01:32:52,484 --> 01:32:54,736
在离这里四英里的田地里。
In a field about four miles from here.

712
01:32:54,819 --> 01:32:57,363
谢谢。吉娜知道。
Grazie. Gina knows where.

713
01:32:57,405 --> 01:33:00,700
我可以开车去吗?——几乎。不会花很长时间的。
- Can I go all the way by car? - Almost. It won't take long.

714
01:33:13,922 --> 01:33:17,342
从科西嘉岛。飞机将在凌晨4点降落。
It's from corsica. The plane will land at 4:00 am.

715
01:33:21,262 --> 01:33:24,891
他们会派什么样的飞机?有多大?
What sort of plane will they send? How big?

716
01:33:24,933 --> 01:33:28,019
他们知道我们有四个人。
They know there are four of us going out.

717
01:33:32,649 --> 01:33:43,576
我知道我应该希望他们快点来，这样一切就都结束了，但我能想到的是，一个小时后我们就要告别了。
I know I should be wishing they'd come quickly and it'll all be over, but all I can think of is, in one hour we'll say good-bye.

718
01:33:43,660 --> 01:33:46,913
吉娜，飞机上还有空位。
Gina, there's room on the plane.

719
01:33:48,456 --> 01:33:52,377
这里的人太少了，即使是一个逃跑的人，也会被严重怀念。
There's so few of us here, even one who runs away is badly missed.

720
01:33:52,418 --> 01:33:55,713
你知道的。你不?
You know that. Don't you?

721
01:33:58,424 --> 01:34:01,553
是的，我知道。
Yes, I know that.

722
01:34:26,494 --> 01:34:28,538
未婚女子polda。
Signorina polda.

723
01:34:43,344 --> 01:34:45,430
Benvenufi。
Benvenufi.

724
01:34:46,931 --> 01:34:49,434
-来吧，小指?祈祷,祝福。
- Come va, pinkie? - Bene, bene.

725
01:34:50,894 --> 01:34:55,690
女士们，女士们，我是波尔达女士
Signori e signora, ia signorina polda

726
01:35:05,116 --> 01:35:10,371
但那不是玛丽亚!
But that's, that's not Maria!

727
01:35:11,372 --> 01:35:14,500
——什么?-那不是玛丽亚!
- What? - That is not Maria!

728
01:35:14,584 --> 01:35:17,545
她在哪里呢?我女儿呢?
Where is she? Where is my daughter?

729
01:35:17,587 --> 01:35:19,589
在佩鲁贾公墓。
In the perugia cemetery.

730
01:35:19,672 --> 01:35:21,758
她六个月前去世了。
She died six months ago.

731
01:35:22,967 --> 01:35:26,554
不。不,那是不可能的。
No. No, that's impossible.

732
01:35:26,596 --> 01:35:28,598
她一直给我写信。
She's been writing me steadily.

733
01:35:29,891 --> 01:35:32,518
这笔迹很难模仿。
The handwriting is so hard to imitate.

734
01:35:43,112 --> 01:35:44,364
德国人!
Germans!

735
01:35:59,379 --> 01:36:02,548
这是没有用的。你被德国人包围了。
It is no use. You're surrounded by Germans.

736
01:36:02,590 --> 01:36:05,718
扔掉你们的枪，举起手走出去。
Throw away your guns and march out with your hands up.

737
01:36:05,802 --> 01:36:08,221
投降。这是你唯一的机会。
Surrender. It's your only chance.

738
01:36:13,601 --> 01:36:14,894
下来!
Get down!

739
01:36:50,096 --> 01:36:52,307
看来他们要慢慢来了。
Looks like they're gonna take their time about it.

740
01:36:52,432 --> 01:36:53,641
他们可以负担得起。
They can afford to.

741
01:36:53,850 --> 01:36:56,769
天亮的时候，他们可能会有一整团德国佬在外面。
They'll probably have a whole kraut regiment out there by daylight.

742
01:36:58,187 --> 01:37:02,150
有时候一个人带球，有时候另一个人。
Ai, sometimes one guy carries the ball, sometimes another.

743
01:37:02,191 --> 01:37:05,486
从地下室出去有条路。
There's a way out of here through the cellar.

744
01:37:06,738 --> 01:37:10,408
-抓住老人和吉娜，快走。-我做不到，小指。
- Grab the old man and Gina and beat it. - I can't do it, pinkie.

745
01:37:15,830 --> 01:37:17,832
现在别对我手软。没有时间。
Don't go soft on me now. There isn't time.

746
01:37:17,874 --> 01:37:20,752
一小时后就天亮了，那架飞机等不及了。
It'll be light in an hour, and that plane can't wait.

747
01:37:22,337 --> 01:37:28,718
-为什么我们不一起试试呢?-你能成功的唯一办法，就是我们开枪让他们相信我们还在这里。
- Why don't we all try it together? - The only way you can make it, is if we do enough shooting to convince them we're all still here.

748
01:37:28,801 --> 01:37:30,720
-快走吧!——不,小手指。
- Now get going! - No, pinkie.

749
01:37:30,803 --> 01:37:33,765
我的命令是带你进入这个国家，然后把你弄出来。
My orders were to get you into this country and get you out.

750
01:37:33,806 --> 01:37:35,725
在这种时候不要对我手软!
Don't go soft on me at a time like this!

751
01:37:35,808 --> 01:37:39,854
吉娜，把他从活板门弄出去。这是命令，你也是
Gina, get him out through the trapdoor. That's an order. For you too, ai

752
01:38:32,782 --> 01:38:34,575
快!快!
Quick! Quick!

753
01:38:46,462 --> 01:38:48,714
光了!
Light out!

754
01:40:25,019 --> 01:40:27,021
Jespeh
Jespeh

755
01:40:29,023 --> 01:40:31,025
吉娜!
Gina!

756
01:42:19,383 --> 01:42:23,846
我只能给他们五分钟。
I can only give them five minutes.

757
01:42:40,905 --> 01:42:42,782
他们来了!
There they come!

758
01:43:37,628 --> 01:43:42,591
-吉娜，姑娘，战后-谁知道会发生什么?
- Gina, girl, after the war - Who knows what'll be then?

759
01:43:42,675 --> 01:43:44,885
我回来了。
I'm coming back.

760
01:43:44,927 --> 01:43:47,221
事物是变化的。
Things change.

761
01:43:47,304 --> 01:43:49,974
——人们改变。-我会回来找你的，吉娜
- People change. - I'm coming back for you, Gina.

762
01:43:50,015 --> 01:43:52,727
谁知道呢?
Who knows?

763
01:43:52,768 --> 01:43:56,605
你不想让我去吗?如果你不喜欢，就说出来。
Don't you want me to? If you don't, say so.

764
01:43:56,689 --> 01:44:00,609
-现在就说。——“希望”?
- Say it now. - "Want"?

765
01:44:00,693 --> 01:44:02,695
“想要”?
"Want"?

766
01:44:05,865 --> 01:44:07,867
超过生活。
More than living.

767
01:44:08,868 --> 01:44:10,786
回来了。
Come back.

768
01:44:10,870 --> 01:44:12,580
回来找我吧。
Come back for me.

769
01:44:21,338 --> 01:44:23,424
再见,亲爱的。
Good-bye, my darling.

770
01:44:37,730 --> 01:44:39,190
我会回来的。
I'll be back.


